{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 789862, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "DeathBlood", "body": "Eitrigg has dialogue with Thrall after turning in the quest [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=9438]Messenger to Thrall[/url].\r\n\r\n\"Eitrigg says: Thrall! My lord... are you all right?\"\r\n\"Thrall says: I'll be fine, Eitrigg. We must begin preparations... I need to go to Outland at once!\"\r\n\"Eitrigg says: With all due respect, Warchief. Our enemies would take advantage of your sudden absence if we don't prepare properly.\"\r\n\"Thrall says: You are right, Eitrigg. The timing is unfavorable. Make sure our best ambassadors are sent as envoys to Hellscream.\"\r\n\"Eitrigg says: At once, sir! For the Horde!\"\r\n\r\n\r\nEitrigg is apparently one of Thrall's trusted advisers, and he shows he is indeed wise.", "date": "2009-07-27T03:57:51-05:00", "rating": 28, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
